ronn\u00e9e. Mouvement ajust\u00e9 dans son bo\u00eetier, dot\u00e9 d\u0027un \u00e9chappement \u00e0 verge et une fus\u00e9e avec corde \u00e0 boyau. Coq \u00e0 un pied, cliquet en acier bleui. Piliers rectilignes.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : Vautroillier Fecit","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"3,9","displayDimension":"3,9 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"2,1","displayDimension":"2,1 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"1","displayDimension":"1 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : cristal de roche\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laiton\r\nMat\u00e9riau : or\r\nTechnique : \u00e9maill\u00e9 = \u00e9maillage = \u00e9mail = \u00e9maux (techniques m\u00e9tal)","placeOfCreation":"Londres (Grande-Bretagne = Grande Bretagne-\u003EAngleterre)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Vente Mrs de Merle, Londres, Christie\u0027s, 6 d\u00e9cembre 1894, n\u00b063, vendu \u00e0 C. Davis, collection Paul Garnier (1834-1916), \u00e0 Paris. Don Paul Garnier, en 1916.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Garnier, Paul ","note":"","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1916","startYear":1916,"endYear":1916}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"don"}],"period":[{"value":"Louis XIII (1610-1643)"},{"value":"Louis XIV (1643-1715)"}],"place":[{"value":"Londres"}],"objectType":[{"value":"horlogerie"},{"value":"montre"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"C